# 2026-01-18 20:06:49.027717
+We are building a play-money online casino inspired by stake.com.
+
+Create a modern Next.js app with:
+- Dark casino UI (neon, glassmorphism)
+- Homepage similar to stake.com with:
+  - featured games
+  - categories (Slots, Originals, Live, New)
+  - game grid with thumbnails
+- User system:
+  - register/login
+  - balance of virtual coins
+  - daily bonus
+- Games:
+  - Dice
+  - Crash
+  - Roulette
+  - Slot machine
+- Each game must:
+  - allow betting virtual coins
+  - show win/loss
+  - update user balance
+- Leaderboard
+- Responsive design
+
+Use Tailwind and modern UI components.
+Store users and balances in a database or local storage for now.
+

